'''洪堡灣'''（'''Humboldt Bay'''）是美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[加利福尼亞北海岸|北海岸]]的一個天然海灣<ref name="HBM-EX">{{cite web  | title =Humboldt Bay Management Plan Executive Summary  | work =  | publisher =Humboldt Bay Harbor Recreation and Conservation District  | date =May 2007  | url =http://www.humboldtbay.org/harbordistrict/documents/hbmp2007/HBM-EXsum_print.pdf  | format =PDF  | doi =  | accessdate =13 December 2012  | deadurl =yes  | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20120224232745/http://www.humboldtbay.org/harbordistrict/documents/hbmp2007/HBM-EXsum_print.pdf  | archivedate =2012年2月24日  }}</ref>和[[潟湖|潟湖]]。<ref name="Costa 2002">{{cite web  | last =Costa  | first =Steven L.  | author2 =Karen A. Glatzel  | title =Coastal Inlets Research Program: Humboldt Bay, California Entrance Channel, Report 1: Data Review  | work =  | publisher =U.S. Army Corps of Engineers  | date =September 2002  | url =http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=ADA409102&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf  | format =PDF  | doi =  | accessdate =13 December 2012  | archive-date =2012-09-29  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120929222833/http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=ADA409102&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf  | dead-url =no  }}</ref> 它整個都位於同名的[[洪堡縣_(加利福尼亞州)|洪堡縣]]內，是[[美國西海岸|美國西海岸]][[舊金山灣|舊金山灣]]到[[普吉特灣|普吉特灣]]之間最大的受保護水體，<ref name="Schlosser">{{cite book  | last =Schlosser  | first =Susan  | author2 =Annie Eicher  | title =Humboldt Bay and Eel River Estuary Benthic Habitat Project  | publisher =California Sea Grant College Program Publication No. T -075  | year =2012  | location =University of California San Diego  | pages =246  | url =http://ca-sgep.ucsd.edu/sites/ca-sgep.ucsd.edu/files/files/Humboldt_Habitats.pdf  | doi =  | id =  | format =PDF  | accessdate =13 December 2009  | deadurl =yes  | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20150402172816/http://ca-sgep.ucsd.edu/sites/ca-sgep.ucsd.edu/files/files/Humboldt_Habitats.pdf  | archivedate =2015年4月2日  }}</ref> 也形成了舊金山和[[庫斯灣|庫斯灣]]之間最大的港口。<ref name="Costa 2002" /> 這個海灣附近最大的城市是[[尤里卡_(加利福尼亞州)|尤里卡]]，加上週邊的聚居地，整個灣區人口將近八萬，即80%的洪堡縣人口。<ref name="TransDevUpdate">{{cite web  | last =  | first =  | title =Draft Transit Dev Plan Humboldt County Systems  | work =  | pages =  | publisher =PMC/HDR  | date =December 2011  | url =http://www.friendlyfortuna.com/DocumentCenter/Home/View/713  | accessdate =23 August 2013  | archive-date =2017-05-25  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170525101241/http://www.friendlyfortuna.com/DocumentCenter/Home/View/713  | dead-url =no  }}</ref> 除去人類的聚居地外，這裡還生活著100多種植物、300多種無脊椎動物、100多種魚類和200多種鳥類。<ref>{{cite web
